,Recommended,247080,24735316,"Posted: 5 August, 2016",all,Skypris,"A beautiful blend of dungeon crawler and rhythm-based gameplay that shows progress isn't the only reward, not with a smashing sountrack like this.To start, I have put over 80hrs in on the PS4 version. That is how I learned of this game. I had to buy it ASAP because that is just how good it is. Even got it on my smartphone and spent about 20 hours on that version.This game tasks you with crawling through a dungeon while slaying monsters to get to the end. Simple enough right? Wrong. To do anything (move, attack, use item) you must do it to the rhythm of the music that is unique to that floor of that dungeon. Sound fun yet? The monsters also have their own movement style that goes to th music too so now you have to learn their pattern to be able to take them out without getting hurt.There are plenty of things to unlock too, like weapons, weapon types, character boosts, and magic items. There are also different characters to unlock in the game that very drasticallly change up how you play your game!Have I mentioned the soundtrack you play to is absolutely amazing?No dungeon crawler is as good as this one. I fear none may ever be. Get out there and buy this!"
