76561198035996343,Recommended,247080,14380517,"Posted: 7 February, 2015",all,Awein,Crypt of the NecroDancer is a unique action platforming puzzle game with a rhythm element.  You are an adventurer trying to kill enemies and all the enemies and you can only move on the beat to the music.  All enemies have different patterns and attacks and there are many enemies moving about while in a zone.  At the time of this review it is still in Beta and there are 3 zones available so far.You have to train yourself to be physically coordinated and quick to process patterns to pass even the first zone.   Most people who have bought this game don't beat zone 1.  There is an option to practice against any specific enemy encountered and this is purchasable with in-game currency.The soundtrack is phenomenal and it will help keep you motivated to keep trying a zone again and again even if there is no success for a while.The game is a unique creative concept with fantastic music that challenges the player physically and mentally.  If you enjoy a challenge and great music it is likely you'll enjoy this game.
