76561198067866896,Recommended,247080,12840456,"Posted: 8 November, 2014",all,secretfreeze,"If you didn't like roguelikes before, well, you do now.If you didn't like rhythm games before, well, you do now.I was a fan of neither and now I'm a fan of both."
